    <h2 style="font-family:var(--font-serif); font-size:clamp(1.8rem, 3.5vw, 2.8rem); font-weight:300; line-height:1.2; color:#191817; margin-bottom:2.5rem;">Common questions about Runcorn.</h2>
    <div style="display:flex; flex-direction:column;">

      <details style="border-bottom:1px solid rgba(72,72,72,0.15); padding:1.25rem 0;">
        <summary style="font-family:var(--font-serif); font-size:1.05rem; cursor:pointer; color:#191817; list-style:none; display:flex; justify-content:space-between; align-items:center; gap:1rem;">
          What drives property values in Runcorn?
          <span style="color:#b98229; font-size:1.4rem; flex-shrink:0;">+</span>
        </summary>
        <p style="font-family:var(--font-sans); font-size:0.9rem; line-height:1.75; color:#4a4540; margin-top:0.75rem; padding-right:2rem;">Runcorn values are driven primarily by the Runcorn State High School catchment, which attracts a consistent and motivated family buyer pool, land size and outdoor space, the suburb's position adjacent to Sunnybank, and Pacific Motorway access. Upgrader families from the inner south are the dominant buyer profile, and they assess properties against a clear set of functional requirements. Properties that meet those requirements clearly and are priced at current market levels attract competitive attention.</p>
      </details>

      <details style="border-bottom:1px solid rgba(72,72,72,0.15); padding:1.25rem 0;">
        <summary style="font-family:var(--font-serif); font-size:1.05rem; cursor:pointer; color:#191817; list-style:none; display:flex; justify-content:space-between; align-items:center; gap:1rem;">
          How long does it take to sell a home in Runcorn?
          <span style="color:#b98229; font-size:1.4rem; flex-shrink:0;">+</span>
        </summary>
        <p style="font-family:var(--font-sans); font-size:0.9rem; line-height:1.75; color:#4a4540; margin-top:0.75rem; padding-right:2rem;">Well-priced Runcorn homes typically sell within 25 to 40 days. The school catchment buyer is among the most decisive in the southern corridor once their criteria are met. Correctly pricing against recent comparable sales and ensuring the property communicates its catchment position clearly are the primary levers for both speed and a strong result.</p>
      </details>

      <details style="border-bottom:1px solid rgba(72,72,72,0.15); padding:1.25rem 0;">
        <summary style="font-family:var(--font-serif); font-size:1.05rem; cursor:pointer; color:#191817; list-style:none; display:flex; justify-content:space-between; align-items:center; gap:1rem;">
          What is the lifestyle like in Runcorn?
          <span style="color:#b98229; font-size:1.4rem; flex-shrink:0;">+</span>
        </summary>
        <p style="font-family:var(--font-sans); font-size:0.9rem; line-height:1.75; color:#4a4540; margin-top:0.75rem; padding-right:2rem;">Runcorn offers a family-oriented lifestyle about fifteen kilometres south of the Brisbane CBD. Parks, community spaces, and school infrastructure make it a functional suburb for families. The proximity to Sunnybank means the food precinct, retail, and community amenity of one of Brisbane's most vibrant multicultural suburbs is a short drive away. Pacific Motorway access makes the CBD and Gold Coast practical commutes, and the settled, owner-occupied character of most of Runcorn's streets contributes to the community feel that families are drawn to.</p>
      </details>

      <details style="padding:1.25rem 0;">
        <summary style="font-family:var(--font-serif); font-size:1.05rem; cursor:pointer; color:#191817; list-style:none; display:flex; justify-content:space-between; align-items:center; gap:1rem;">
          What is my Runcorn home worth in 2026?
          <span style="color:#b98229; font-size:1.4rem; flex-shrink:0;">+</span>
        </summary>
        <p style="font-family:var(--font-sans); font-size:0.9rem; line-height:1.75; color:#4a4540; margin-top:0.75rem; padding-right:2rem;">Runcorn values in 2026 reflect the suburb's school catchment position, land size, outdoor space, and street character as the primary variables. Upgrader buyers assess properties against functional family living standards, which means preparation quality and presentation clarity directly influence price outcomes. Contact Daniel for a current appraisal based on recent comparable sales and an honest read of how your property sits in the current market.</p>
      </details>

    </div>
  </div>
</section>

